
#########################
# Installation / Config #
#########################

1) copy files from "eshop" to your shop

#####	
2) Add the following module-entries in your configuration

	oxoutput => marm/piwik/marm_piwik_oxoutput

	
#####	
3) Set up your PIWIK variables in Master Settings > Core Settings > Piwik setup

	Piwik URL should be without piwik.php ending. like "www.example.org/piwik/"

#####
4) Clean your language cache (cleanup eShop tmp directory)



If you don't see Master Settings > Core Settings > Piwik setup tab, logout and login again to admin section.